Personality/motivation: A warm person, easily to get along with. Has unparalleled leadership and diplomatic skills. He is sly with his words, and cunning with his actions. His eyes seem to stare into the very soul of the person. Also able to predict the future, but not always accurate. Has the unique ability to see peoples weaknesses.<br>
