<br>
Magic: Fire adept. Fire empowers him, and heals him. <br>
<br>
Magik: Nature. Has the ability to talk with the creatures and bring them under his command. Has a pet tiger who follows him everywhere. When in natural surroundings is tougher to beat, when in cities weaker.<br>
<br>
Weapon/s: Dual Katana's.<br>
<br>
History: A man who grew up in Elarea, the realm of chaos, civil war, and turmoil. He made many allies, and with his great use of words and grand tactics became one of the main powers in Elarea. He made strong allies and in time acheived the dream all had hoped for. Elarea was united, Militant as the new emporer of Elarea. At first things were peacful, but then small quarells for power arised. An assassination was planned, and Militant died the same way as the late King Eagle. He was remembered in legend and has come back from the heavens to end the chaos once again. <p>Don't fear that which you do not know I wont hurt you</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bgoergyboysroleplayingpalace.showUserPublicProfile?gid=goergyboy>Goergyboy</A> at: 10/27/03 10:57 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bgoergyboysroleplayingpalace.showUserPublicProfile?gid=djsooguy>djsooguy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fresh Meat</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#0000FF>(10/29/03 12:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Character Profile</span><hr size=1> OK! ILL JOIN! STOP BOTHERING ME!<br>
